############################################################
#               control file for ASTR  code                #
############################################################

# lwrite,lavg                : switch for IO and on-fly sta
f,f,f

# maxstep,nwrite,ninst,nlstep,navg : parameters
1000,1000,50,1,50

# deltat                    : time step
1.8d-3

# The controller file will be read during a simulation, 
# everytime after dumping checkpoint.

#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|        lwrite | to output flowfield sequence            |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|        lwslce | to output flowfield at given i/j/k cut  |
#|               | , slice.dat will be required to define  |
#|               |  i/j/k position                         |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|          lavg | to calculate statistics and also output |
#|               | meanflow, 2order and 3order files.      |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|        nwrite | frequency of outputting flow field and  |
#|               | checkpoint                              |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|         ninst | frequency of writing slices             |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|        nlstep | frequency of updating log file          |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|          navg | frequency of calculating statistics     |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+
#|        deltat | the time step                           |
#+---------------+-----------------------------------------+